      "title": "MONGODB ALERT: Bragar Eagel & Squire, P.C. is Investigating MongoDB, Inc. on Behalf of Long-Term Stockholders and Encourages Investors to Contact the Firm",
      "summary": "Law firm Bragar Eagel & Squire is investigating MongoDB's board of directors for potential breach of fiduciary duties following significant stock price declines. MongoDB reported strong Q4 2023 results but issued lower-than-expected 2025 guidance in March 2024 due to changes in sales incentive structure, causing a $28.59 stock drop. In May 2024, further guidance cuts attributed to macro conditions resulted in a $73.94 per share decline. Long-term stockholders between August 31, 2023 and May 30, 2024 are encouraged to contact the firm.",
